        </div>
Lease at the Selden! Located between Cass and Second, all the amenities that the City has to offer are at your fingertips.This luxury condo development with a design-forward appeal features beautiful top-of-the-line finishes that set this apart from the rest of the market! This 2BR. 2 Bath unit features keyless entry, marble baths, quartz countertops, and sleek European custom cabinets throughout. Enjoy a chef's kitchen with an open concept, including a quartz waterfall island backdrop. This unit boasts 10 foot ceilings and a beautiful balcony with west facing windows. The roof-top lounge features a dog run and wash station and amazing views of the City. One indoor climate controlled parking space with EV Charger is included. Walk downstairs to the award-winning restaurant, SheWolf!  <br>
<br>
<br>
The main floor boasts an amazing master suite that you will fall in love with. The private master bathroom has a large tub, separate shower, double sinks and a large walk-in closet. The living room has an open concept and a cozy fireplace for your family to enjoy during the cool winter evenings.<br>
<br>
TO APPLY we will need:<br>
1. Completed application -- get your application from the Office!<br>
2. Photo ID<br>
3. Proof of income for the last 30 days<br>
4. $1 (application fee) This does get applied to your deposit upon approval!<br>
<br>
Amenities include:<br>
2 Large Pools<br>
Pet Friendly<br>
Laundry On-Site<br>
24/7 On-Call Maintenance<br>
Picnic Tables<br>
Grilling Area<br>
Trash, Water, &amp; Pest Control Paid. You only pay electricity for utilities!<br>
Easy highway access<br>
Easily set up Net Fiber Internet<br>
Parking Off-Street
    </section>

